the numbers are time interval between first and second frame in nanoseconds
working                                                                          1117000
while-1-after-initialize-eor-interrupt-only-once 714313000-843256000          5128943000
while-1-after-initialize                                                      5064936000
while-1-after-initialize-without-epen-in-eor-handler 930313000-931420000         1107000

conclusion: if we do not do EPEN in eor handler, zero response packet is sent, otherwise it waits
data to be loaded (if it is not loaded, zero response packet is sent)
